\((x, y, z)\)デカルト座標系から\((R, \varphi, z)\)円筒座標系に移ったときの\((\pi^{ij})\)の成分を、同様に\(\pi^{RR}, \pi^{\varphi z}, \pi^{Rz}\)などのように書くことにします。 デカルト座標で\(\mathbf{v} = (v_x, v_y, v_z), \mathbf{B} = (B_x, B_y, B_z)\)と記述されるベクトルを円筒座標系の成分に書き換えると . \[\left\{  egin{array}{l} v_R = v_x \cos \varphi + v_y \sin \varphi \ v_\varphi = -v_x \sin \varphi + v_y \cos \varphi \ v_z = v_z \end{array} ight., \quad \left\{  egin{array}{l} B_R = B_x \cos \varphi + B_y \sin \varphi \ B_\varphi = -B_x \sin \varphi + B_y \cos \varphi \ B_z = B_z \end{array} ight. 	ag{6}\] のようになります。 円筒座標での\(\pi^{ij}\)を求める前に以下の量を計算しておきましょう。\((x, y, z)\)と\((R, \varphi, z)\)との間には . \[\left\{  egin{array}{l} x = R \cos \varphi \ y = R \sin \varphi \ z = z \end{array} ight. \ \Longrightarrow \ \left\{  egin{array}{l} x^2 + y^2 = R^2 \ 	an \varphi =  rac{y}{x} \ z = z \end{array} ight. 	ag{7}\] のような関係があります。これより . \[2 x = 2R  rac{\partial R}{\partial x} \ \Longrightarrow \  rac{\partial R}{\partial x} =  rac{x}{R} = \cos \varphi 	ag{8}\] \[2 y = 2R  rac{\partial R}{\partial y} \ \Longrightarrow \  rac{\partial R}{\partial y} =  rac{y}{R} = \sin \varphi 	ag{9}\] \[ rac{1}{\cos^2 \varphi}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x} = -  rac{y}{x^2} = -  rac{R \sin \varphi}{R^2 \cos^2 \varphi} \ \Longrightarrow \  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x} = -  rac{\sin \varphi}{R} 	ag{10}\] \[ rac{1}{\cos^2 \varphi}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y} =  rac{1}{x} =  rac{1}{R \cos \varphi} \ \Longrightarrow \  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y} = -  rac{\cos \varphi}{R} 	ag{11}\] \[ rac{\partial R}{\partial z} =  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z} =  rac{\partial z}{\partial x} =  rac{\partial z}{\partial y} = 0 	ag{12}\] \[ rac{\partial z}{\partial z} = 1 	ag{13}\] これらを用いて具体的に\(\pi\)の\((R, \varphi, z)\)での形を求めていきましょう。2階のテンソルの成分の変換則は . \[\pi^{i'j'} =  rac{\partial x^{i'}}{\partial x^k}  rac{\partial x^{j'}}{\partial x^\ell} \pi^{k \ell} 	ag{14}\] のように与えられるので . \[ egin{align} \pi^{RR} &amp;=  rac{\partial R}{\partial x}  rac{\partial R}{\partial x} \pi^{xx} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial x}  rac{\partial R}{\partial y} \pi^{xy} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial x}  rac{\partial R}{\partial z} \pi^{xz} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial y}  rac{\partial R}{\partial x} \pi^{yx} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial y}  rac{\partial R}{\partial y} \pi^{yy} 
otag \ &amp; \qquad +  rac{\partial R}{\partial y}  rac{\partial R}{\partial z} \pi^{yz} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial z}  rac{\partial R}{\partial x} \pi^{zx} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial z}  rac{\partial R}{\partial y} \pi^{zy} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial z}  rac{\partial R}{\partial z} \pi^{zz} 
otag \ &amp;= \pi^{xx} \cos^2 \varphi + \pi^{xy} \cos \varphi \sin \varphi + \pi^{yx} \sin \varphi \cos \varphi + \pi^{yy} \sin^2 \varphi 
otag \ &amp;= P_\mathrm{gm} + ho(v_x \cos \varphi + v_y \sin\varphi)^2 -  rac{1}{4\pi} (B_x \cos \varphi + B_y \sin \varphi)^2 = P_\mathrm{gm} + ho v_R^2 -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_R^2 	ag{15} \end{align}\] \[ egin{align} \pi^{R\varphi} &amp;=  rac{\partial R}{\partial x}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x} \pi^{xx} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial x}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y} \pi^{xy} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial x}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z} \pi^{xz} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial y}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x} \pi^{yx} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial y}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y} \pi^{yy} 
otag \ &amp; \qquad +  rac{\partial R}{\partial y}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z} \pi^{yz} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial z}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x} \pi^{zx} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial z}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y} \pi^{zy} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial z}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z} \pi^{zz} 
otag \ &amp;= -  rac{\cos \varphi \sin \varphi}{R} \pi^{xx} +  rac{\cos^2 \varphi}{R} \pi^{xy} -  rac{\sin^2 \varphi}{R} \pi^{yx} +  rac{\sin \varphi \cos \varphi}{R} \pi^{yy} 
otag \ &amp;=  rac{1}{R} \left\{ ho v_\varphi (v_x \cos \varphi + v_y \sin \varphi) -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_\varphi (B_x \cos \varphi + B_y \sin \varphi) ight\} =  rac{1}{R} \left( ho v_R v_\varphi -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_R B_\varphi ight) 	ag{16} \end{align}\] \[ egin{align} \pi^{Rz} &amp;=  rac{\partial R}{\partial x}  rac{\partial z}{\partial x} \pi^{xx} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial x}  rac{\partial z}{\partial y} \pi^{xy} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial x}  rac{\partial z}{\partial z} \pi^{xz} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial y}  rac{\partial z}{\partial x} \pi^{yx} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial y}  rac{\partial z}{\partial y} \pi^{yy} 
otag \ &amp; \qquad +  rac{\partial R}{\partial y}  rac{\partial z}{\partial z} \pi^{yz} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial z}  rac{\partial z}{\partial x} \pi^{zx} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial z}  rac{\partial z}{\partial y} \pi^{zy} +  rac{\partial R}{\partial z}  rac{\partial z}{\partial z} \pi^{zz} 
otag \ &amp;= \pi^{xz} \cos \varphi + \pi^{yz} \sin \varphi 
otag \ &amp;= ho v_z (v_x \cos \varphi + v_y \sin \varphi) -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_z(B_x \cos \varphi + B_y \sin \varphi) = ho v_R v_z -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_R B_z 	ag{17} \end{align}\] \[ egin{align} \pi^{\varphi \varphi} &amp;=  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x} \pi^{xx} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y} \pi^{xy} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z} \pi^{xz} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x} \pi^{yx} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y} \pi^{yy} 
otag \ &amp; \qquad +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z} \pi^{yz} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x} \pi^{zx} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y} \pi^{zy} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z} \pi^{zz} 
otag \ &amp;=  rac{\sin^2 \varphi}{R^2} \pi^{xx} -  rac{\sin \varphi \cos \varphi}{R^2} \pi^{xy} -  rac{\cos \varphi \sin \varphi}{R^2} \pi^{yx} +  rac{\cos^2 \varphi}{R^2} \pi^{yy} 
otag \ &amp;=  rac{1}{R^2} \left\{ P_\mathrm{gm} + (v_x \sin \varphi - v_y \cos \varphi)^2 -  rac{1}{4\pi} (B_x \sin \varphi - B_y \cos \varphi)^2ight\} =  rac{1}{R^2} \left( P_\mathrm{gm} + ho v_\varphi^2 -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_\varphi^2 ight) 	ag{18} \end{align}\] \[ egin{align} \pi^{\varphi z} &amp;=  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x}  rac{\partial z}{\partial x} \pi^{xx} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x}  rac{\partial z}{\partial y} \pi^{xy} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x}  rac{\partial z}{\partial z} \pi^{xz} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y}  rac{\partial z}{\partial x} \pi^{yx} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y}  rac{\partial z}{\partial y} \pi^{yy} 
otag \ &amp;\qquad +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y}  rac{\partial z}{\partial z} \pi^{yz} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z}  rac{\partial z}{\partial x} \pi^{zx} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z}  rac{\partial z}{\partial y} \pi^{zy} +  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z}  rac{\partial z}{\partial z} \pi^{zz} 
otag \ &amp;= -  rac{\sin \varphi}{R} \pi^{xz} +  rac{\cos \varphi}{R} \pi^{yz} 
otag \ &amp;=  rac{1}{R} \left( ho v_\varphi v_z -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_\varphi B_zight) 	ag{19} \end{align}\] \(\pi^{zz}\)は変わらずそのままであること、そして . \[\pi^{\varphi R} =  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x^k}  rac{\partial R}{\partial x^\ell} \pi^{k \ell} =  rac{\partial R}{\partial x^\ell}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x^k} \pi^{k \ell} =  rac{\partial R}{\partial x^k}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x^\ell} \underbrace{\pi^{\ell k}}_{(5)より対称テンソル} = \pi^{R\varphi} 	ag{20}\] などより、これらをまとめて . \[(\pi^{ij}) = \left(  egin{array}{ccc} \pi^{RR} &amp; \pi^{R\varphi} &amp; \pi^{Rz} \ \pi^{\varphi R} &amp; \pi^{\varphi \varphi} &amp; \pi^{\varphi z} \ \pi^{zR} &amp; \pi^{z\varphi} &amp; \pi^{zz} \end{array}ight) = \left(  egin{array}{ccc} P_\mathrm{gm} + ho v_R^2 -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_R^2 &amp;  rac{1}{R} \left( ho v_R v_\varphi -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_R B_\varphi ight) &amp; v_R v_z -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_R B_z \  rac{1}{R} \left( ho v_\varphi v_R -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_\varphi B_R ight) &amp;  rac{1}{R^2} \left( P_\mathrm{gm} + ho v_\varphi^2 -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_\varphi^2 ight) &amp;  rac{1}{R} \left( ho v_\varphi v_z -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_\varphi B_zight) \ ho v_z v_R -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_z B_R &amp;  rac{1}{R} \left( ho v_z v_\varphi -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_z B_\varphi ight) &amp; P_\mathrm{gm} + ho v_z^2 -  rac{1}{4\pi} B_z^2 \end{array} ight) 	ag{21}\] .

