partial z} = - 2  rac{x^2 + y^2}{z^2}  rac{1}{z} = - 2 	an^2 	heta  rac{1}{r \cos 	heta} \ \Longrightarrow \  rac{\partial 	heta}{\partial z} = -  rac{\sin 	heta}{r} 	ag{13}\] \[ rac{1}{\cos^2 \varphi}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x} = -  rac{y}{x^2} = -  rac{r \sin 	heta \sin \varphi}{r^2 \sin^2 	heta \cos^2 \varphi} \ \Longrightarrow \  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial x} = -  rac{\sin \varphi}{r \sin 	heta} 	ag{14}\] \[ rac{1}{\cos^2 \varphi}  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y} =  rac{1}{x} =  rac{1}{r \sin 	heta \cos \varphi} \ \Longrightarrow \  rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial y} =  rac{\cos \varphi}{r \sin 	heta} 	ag{15}\] \[ rac{\partial \varphi}{\partial z} = 0 	ag{16}\] これらを用いて具体的に\(\pi\)の\((r, 	heta, \varphi)\)での形を求めていきましょう。2階のテンソルの成分の変換則は . \[\pi^{i'j'} =  rac{\partial x^{i'}}{\partial x^k}  rac{\partial x^{j'}}{\partial x^\ell} \pi^{k \ell} 	ag{17}\] のように与えられるので . \[ egin{align} \pi^{rr} &amp;=  rac{\partial r}{\partial x}  rac{\partial r}{\partial x} \pi^{xx} +  rac{\partial r}{\partial x}  rac{\partial r}{\partial y} \pi^{xy} +  rac{\partial r}{\partial x}  rac{\partial r}{\partial z} \pi^{xz} +  rac{\partial r}{\partial y}  rac{\partial r}{\partial x} \pi^{yx} +  rac{\partial r}{\partial y}  rac{\partial r}{\partial y} \pi^{yy} 
